HOW TO RUN
Android native
PLATFORM=android ENVIRONMENT=local npx wdio

Android mobile web
PLATFORM=android MOBILE_WEB=true npx wdio

iOS mobile web
PLATFORM=ios MOBILE_WEB=true npx wdio

iOS native
PLATFORM=ios npx wdio
OR
android
PLATFORM=android npx wdio

RUN ALL TESTS
PLATFORM=browser npx wdio




Browser
PLATFORM=browser BROWSER=chrome npx wdio
OR
PLATFORM=browser BROWSER=firefox npx wdio
OR
PLATFORM=browser BROWSER=safari npx wdio





